definitions.definition: An operation in which data is transmitted .
An icon (usually on a computer screen and labeled with the word "Send") on which one clicks (with a mouse or its equivalent ) or taps to transmit an email or other electronic message .
examples: Good thing I didn't hit send on that resume; I just noticed a bad typo.
definitions.label_groups: graphical user interface ; often capitalized , or capitalized and put in quotation marks

definitions.definition: A messenger , especially one sent to fetch the bride .
A callout or diss usually aimed at a specific person, often in the form of a diss track .
A successful ascent of a sport climbing route.

main_definition: ( telecommunications ) An operation in which data is transmitted .
